(38889, 20951, 0, 1, 'Tears of the victims (EP Version)', '「Tears Of The Victims」，獻給那些家國的存亡曾在恐懼籠罩之下，卻仍擁有希望的人們，知道自己或許沒有辦法改變，卻還是願意為了迎接未來的到來而犧牲，無懼死亡的背水一戰。', '2011-06-18 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 9, ' Tears Of The Victims\r\n\r\n詞、曲：Eye  Of  Violence\r\n編曲：Eye  Of  Violence\r\n\r\nUnder a cover of clouds and rains\r\nThere was a wonderland\r\nthe glory, happiness, all the hope and dreams mean everything to me\r\nSomehow a drastic change occurred\r\nfaith collapse, like glass falling into pieces\r\n\r\nSacrifice, those tear drops in the eyes\r\nsay good bye, from the moment we''re\r\nFearless, \r\nwe would be barely hanging on though\r\nstill worth to give our life for.\r\n\r\nThe day of freedom would start same as we falling apart\r\n\r\nI saw death approaching toward right where we are\r\nbut there''s also light come from heaven\r\n\r\nI saw death approaching toward right where we are\r\nwhat would it take? we would be barely hanging.\r\n\r\nThat''s why(We Fight)\r\nFor All (We Share)\r\nTill it comes to the end, we falling apart\r\nThis is why (We Fight)\r\nwithout asking(What left for me)\r\nThe day will come, this all will be done. \r\n\r\nThat is why we fight for all we share\r\nsay goodbye, we say goodbye,\r\n we will live till it comes to the end\r\nwe falling apart, and this is what we fight for\r\nthe day will come, this all will be done.\r\n\r\n', '', 252, '', 'Eye  Of  Violence', 'Eye  Of  Violence', 'Eye  Of  Violence', 'Eye  Of  Violence', '', 1, 1, 0, '2011-09-18 02:57:45', '2015-03-12 13:48:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
